The `Proteomics.analysis.data` package was prepared by the 
MRC Toxicology unit  and Proteomics and
[bioinformaticsfacilities](https://github.com/MRCToxBioinformatics) to 
provide data for training sessions covering the basics of proteomics analyses.

## Install

```{r, eval=FALSE}
remotes::install_github("MRCToxBioinformatics/Proteomics.analysis.data")
```
